00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/at-the-colosseum-new-marble-slabs-mark-where-towering-columns-stood-thousands-of-years-ago-180988378/</guid></item><item><title>英格兰的“康斯特布尔之国”将举办为期一年的展览，庆祝其同名景观艺术家约翰·康斯特布尔 (John Constable) 诞辰 250 周年</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/englands-constable-country-is-honoring-the-250th-birthday-of-its-namesake-landscape-artist-john-constable-with-a-year-of-exhibitions-180988381/</link><description>康斯特布尔于 1776 年 6 月 11 日出生于萨福克郡的东伯格霍特村。附近的伊普斯威奇以“康斯特布尔 250”来纪念这位田园画家与其祖国、社区、国家和当代艺术的联系</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 19:44:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/englands-constable-country-is-honoring-the-250th-birthday-of-its-namesake-landscape-artist-john-constable-with-a-year-of-exhibitions-180988381/</guid></item><item><title>一名场地管理员注意到高尔夫球场上有一个污水坑。原来是一个装满空瓶的酒窖，100多年来未曾动过</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/a-groundskeeper-noticed-a-sinkhole-on-a-golf-course-it-turned-out-to-be-a-wine-cellar-full-of-empty-bottles-untouched-for-more-than-100-years-180988379/</link><description>该酒窖位于英格兰达维休姆公园高尔夫俱乐部球场的第 13 洞附近。工作人员认为它以前是一座庄园的一​​部分，于 1888 年被拆除</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 19:04:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/a-groundskeeper-noticed-a-sinkhole-on-a-golf-course-it-turned-out-to-be-a-wine-cellar-full-of-empty-bottles-untouched-for-more-than-100-years-180988379/</guid></item><item><title>实验性大脑植入物可以让瘫痪患者用大脑表达自己的想法</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/an-experimental-brain-implant-allows-people-with-paralysis-to-type-their-thoughts-with-their-minds-180988365/</link><description>两名参与者之一的写字速度类似于健全人在智能手机上发短信的速度</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 18:47:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/an-experimental-brain-implant-allows-people-with-paralysis-to-type-their-thoughts-with-their-minds-1